{"tid":1566180,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民建聯晤黃偉綸 稱同意更多用《收回土地條例》","createTime":"2019-09-13T12:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T00:53:26.000Z","uid":144018,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a1e73f733fb838c4a859beac5fbe409835b110a7","tid":1566180,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:49:47.000Z","msg":"//...民建聯上午與發展局長黃偉綸見面，建議更積極使用《收回土地條例》，加快覓地建屋速度，以達到3年上樓目標。民建聯主席李慧琼向傳媒表示，會上黃偉綸反應正面，認同民建聯提出更積極引用《收回土地條例》，又說政府在過去一段時間已尋覓逾200幅土地作積極研究。此外，民建聯又建議政府要與迪士尼的營運者商討，將迪士尼擴建的二、三期土地用作興建公營房屋...//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TourisMan.hk/posts/2531446180465336\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTourisMan.hk%2Fposts%2F2531446180465336&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88gZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=babca248\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TourisMan.hk/posts/2531446180465336</a><br />\n<br />\n一聽到人話，就知選舉近了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a78c4605d5256722bffc1a80433af60aec0d25","tid":1566180,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:50:01.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthrHTWT.jpg&h=21d791c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab358f5e55e13f952ee80f45493c4a4bdb55458e","tid":1566180,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:50:26.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h